quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,51,"[Hay] si Min nulii henndu, …ďe yi'i [gese ma…ď…ďe] …óen no soy…ói, …ďe njokkay …ďaawo …óuum, he…ďe njedda."
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maay…ďe …ďen, a nanintaa fa'a…óu…ďe …ďeen kadi noddaandu ndun, si …ďe nduŇčtiima …ďe huccinii …ďabbe (ma…ď…ďe)."
  30,53,"A wonaani pewnoowo wum…ďe …ďen e majjere ma…ď…ďe. A nanintaa si wonaa …ďeen gooŇč…óim…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, hara ko …ďe jebbilii…ďe."
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni tak…óo on e lo'ere, refti O wa…ói …ďaawo lo'ere nde semmbe, refti o wa…ói …ďaawo cemmbe …óen lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Homo taga ko O muuyi, Ko KaŇčko woni ganndu…óo, kattan…óo."
  30,55,"√Ďande Darngal nal darotoo, bon…ďe …ďen ngoo…óndat …ďe √Īii…ďaani si wonaa saanga. Ko wano nii …ďe wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)."
  30,56,"Okkaa…ďe ganndal e gooŇč…óinal …ďeen mbi'a: "GooŇč…óii on √Īii…ďii e ko Alla winndi kon, haa √Īande ummital. Ko ndee woni √Īalaande ummital, kono onon on nganndaano"."
  30,57,"Nden √Īande, ngantooji …óin nafoytaa too√Īu…ďe …ďeen, wonaa kam…ďe woni ko …óa…ď…ďiretee welayee [Alla]."
  30,58,"GooŇč…óii Min piyanii yim…ďe …ďen e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii …ďe Aaya, …ďen yeddu…ďe mbi'at: "On ngonaani, si wonaa meerentee…ďe"."
  30,59,"Ko wano nii Alla notira e …ďer…óe …ďe …ďe nganndaa."
  30,60,"Mu√Ī√Īo, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goonga. Wota …ďe njananaaka …ďe koyfine."